# AstroAI hints for Goose (project-level: copy to .goosehints in repo root)

Use rg/fd/gh before asking for full file reads. Code lives in TMP_SRC_DIR (/srcdir); stage data on TMP_SCRATCH_DIR (/scratch).
Install deps with pixi install or uv sync (lockfiles in this repo). Push git or run canfar-lab push --yes before the session ends.
Platform CLIs (canfar, cadcget, canfar-lab): /opt/astroai/venv/cadc — upgrade-cadc-tools.sh for in-session bumps.
For Python: pixi run python … or uv run python … from the project root.
